Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.99,0:01:41.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,On my wedding day, I passed through\Nthe forest to the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:46.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe that's when it attached itself to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:56.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was there all of a sudden, a green thing, on my gown.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:01:59.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was only after the wedding that I noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:03.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seemed very vile.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:08.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The following year, I gave birth to my first child.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:14.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my boy – Watahiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:18.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's been getting weaker and weaker\Nsince the stains began to appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:21.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every time I see it, I remember that stain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:27.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forgive me if I'm wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:33.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did he have a human form when he was born?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:39.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:45.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't even resemble an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:54.27,ep-title-bg,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2100,0)\p1\blur1}m 0 0 l 950 0 950 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.27,0:02:54.27,ep-title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2100,0)\be1}Cotton Changeling
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:03:00.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd be called back to\Ntheir home only three months later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:11.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:13.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank god you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:15.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you read the letter? Did I make it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Come in, quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:20.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:25.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I meant to do as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's fine. Thanks for letting me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:33.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But honestly, I never thought it would happen so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:34.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:37.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's growing frighteningly fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:45.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did he have a human form when he was born?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:49.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aki, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:59.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't even an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:09.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It didn't even cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:14.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a green, formless {\i1}thing{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:17.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:18.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:22.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:35.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It slipped into the floor in the blink\Nof an eye and disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:39.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife wanted a child dearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:45.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then she gave up and became depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:51.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And one year later...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:56.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:58.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it from under the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:08.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone must have abandoned him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:12.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. It's that child from back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:15.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:18.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He looks a lot like Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:22.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must have grown to take a human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:29.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inside, I was terrified, but I convinced\Nmyself to believe her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:35.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This child, Watahiko, grew quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:40.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He loved small fish and berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:45.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In just over six months, he grew\Nto the size of a three year old.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:48.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he still had the mind of a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:54.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Emotionless and without speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:59.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he came to look more and more like us,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:01.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and we became attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:06.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,One night...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:12.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that a cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:14.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it, it's annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:24.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was another baby under the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:29.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's just like Watahiko in every way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:32.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll have to raise him the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:35.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe we'll have more?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:38.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say that, that's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:45.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watahiko was born again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:50.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tried digging underneath the floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:54.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I never found anything odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:07:00.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This year though, something odd\Nhappened to our first born.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:07.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Green stains appeared on his skin,\Nand he'd sleep for most of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:10.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our doctor gave up completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:15.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we heard that you may be able to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:21.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, we Mushi-shi can't save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:25.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the end of his lifespan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:29.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a Mushi called Watahaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:33.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They float around in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:37.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They invade the wombs of pregnant\Nhuman women and infest the egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:40.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They are born as a pile of goo,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:44.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and quickly escape into floors and ceilings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:49.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A year later, they send a "Hitotake" to the person's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:54.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The timeline of their births matches\Nthe Watahaki's pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:58.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though, can I check under your floor just in case?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:02.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No thanks, I don't need a light.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:06.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:09.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's huge too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:13.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No mistake. It's a Watahaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way. I don't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look carefully at this dirt in the sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:28.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hitotake are connected to the Mushi's\Nmain body by a thread-like bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:36.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're just part of the Mushi, sending nutrients to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:40.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:44.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That boy will soon have finished\Nhis task and undergo necrolysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:48.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he dies, his body will emit\Na huge number of "spores".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:52.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll have to kill him before that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:54.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:58.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you think I called you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:02.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Save him from that Mushi thing you speak of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:06.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is no "child" for me to save.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:12.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those "children" are Mushi bearing your likeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:19.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And these are what killed your true child-to-be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:22.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please. You have to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:32.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:36.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have a right to despise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:46.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for convincing your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:51.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She still won't even talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:54.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've raised him for over three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:56.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:02.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she wants to keep the rest of the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:05.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I beg you! Let them live!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:08.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're harmless until they become sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:09.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:15.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before our second and the next child emit their spores,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:17.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:25.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watahaki have a life expectancy of ten to thirty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:28.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no telling how long this'll go on
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:33.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,or how many "children" you'll have to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:36.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you still do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:37.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:39.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:46.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said you were terrified of those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:49.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you still want to raise them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:56.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just don't want to make my wife sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:11:00.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aki truly adores the remaining four.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:07.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no telling what'll happen to her if we lose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:15.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was married before to a large retailer's\Nfamily beyond the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:20.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over there, she gave birth to their son and heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:25.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he died in less than a year in a stupid accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:29.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They divorced because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:31.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:34.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can it be so cruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:43.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Up until now, every child known to be\Na Watahaki's child was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:47.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, they let the roots run dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:53.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not one was ever allowed to live after the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:58.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They might change for the worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:11:59.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:01.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:03.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,they might not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:11.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't like killing everything I'm\Nnot sure about. It's too blunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:14.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't stay here to watch,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:17.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I'll be back within three months\Nto see how things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:20.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Send a letter there if something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:22.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:25.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't thank you enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:30.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in less than three months, a letter came.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:33.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:36.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:37.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:39.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:41.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:45.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watahiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:57.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:13:02.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife finally seems to agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:04.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're raising an abomination.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:07.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got to do what we've got to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:11.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aki, Ginko's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:17.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:20.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:21.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:22.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:34.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:36.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:47.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow. Ow. Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:49.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:53.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanna leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:55.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:14:00.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll keep her in the bedroom until it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that'd help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:08.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought she understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:14.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems like things have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:19.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I was going to tell you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:25.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not just that they're growing faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:30.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,One time, our fourth was cracking nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:32.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd only taught our second one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It took our second child a long time to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:37.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must have learned from watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:42.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They seem to have begun to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:48.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're drenched. Let's get you changed right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:51.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:56.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Daddy, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:15:00.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aki, he's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:04.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah? I'll get you something to eat right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:10.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then our second child began showing those symptons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:13.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:18.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}just{\i0} happened to our other child.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:20.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:24.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's our duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:30.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Daddy, I'm afraid to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:33.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't kill me. Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:43.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd become a human thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:47.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We couldn't do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:50.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,even if it was my child's enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:54.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They've gained cognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:58.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, they must have been capable all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:03.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They might have experienced fear\Nafter the first one's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:08.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And their individual knowledge is being\Nshared amongst all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:13.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Each are parts of a whole connected at the roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:17.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They obtain five times the amount\Nof information at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They'll learn fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:24.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But... "human-thing"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:32.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, what lives in his mind is only a thinking spore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:36.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:39.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to get killed. We're going to get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:45.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have to protect the seed. I think there's a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:49.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't remember. I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:52.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I learned how to speak and now I can't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:57.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The seed... How do we protect the seed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:16.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:21.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I can sorta stay up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:23.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:26.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your second child's in the inner room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:35.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll destroy the root and\Ntake the rest of the "children".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:40.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't leave them with you any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:55.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help me. Don't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:57.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:58.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:01.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you going to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:04.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you consume human children.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:06.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not our fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:08.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not our fault either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:11.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we're stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:15.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're going to die along with your seed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:20.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:24.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:26.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:28.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:41.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those bastards... They're going to burn the entire root.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:49.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. Did you kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:52.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I read it on the scroll that you had.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:56.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Normally, we could do it instinctively.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:19:00.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the only way we can protect the seed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:06.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:08.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't come in! Go outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:11.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watahiko... Where are the children?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:13.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They{\i0} set the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:16.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'll do anything to protect the seed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what those Mushi do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:20.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They are my children now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:22.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:26.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watahiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:28.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watahiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:54.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watahiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watahiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:13.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The root's completely gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:26.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Watahaki are in danger, they disconnect\Nthe Hitotake from the roots
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:29.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and attempt to save the seed at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:34.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Hitotake change form and enter a long sleep state.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:42.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:45.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know when they'll be reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:49.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might be after you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:54.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In either case, I'll leave it with you until the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:20:58.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:02.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:15.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you give them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:16.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:19.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was supposed to keep me fed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:20.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:24.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:27.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a strange being.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:29.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look who's talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:33.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you supposed to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:36.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what it says in all the records.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:40.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno. I'm not sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:45.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why haven't you killed me yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:49.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:54.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a strange being.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:57.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever, just go to sleep already.
